n: Chicken and White Cheddar Queso Chili
des: "Take some everyday pantry items and just a few minutes to serve your family a warm, comforting bowl of chicken chili! Suggested garnishes: fresh cilantro, chopped scallions, tortilla chips. This would be very good with a pan of cornbread!"
ins: Combine beans, chicken broth, chicken breast, salsa verde, rice mix, chili powder, cumin, and garlic powder in a large saucepan over medium heat. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, until rice is tender, about 7 minutes. Stir and remove from heat. Let stand before serving, about 2 minutes.
